		<div id="p770" class="post altstyle" data-posted="1302144246" data-group-id="1">
			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p770" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>2</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://lestnitsa.bbmy.ru/viewtopic.php?id=177#p770">Чт, 7 Апр 2011 06:44</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<IDXSKIP><div class="post-author">
					<ul>
						<li class="pa-author"><span class="acchide">Автор:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://lestnitsa.bbmy.ru/profile.php?id=2" rel="nofollow">гл</a></li>
